The C/C++ Development Tooling (CDT) are a set of Eclipse plugin-ins which
provied a fully featured C/C++ IDE. The main focus of the CDT is to support
the freely available open source compilers and tools, such as the
GNU Tools: GCC, GDB and Make.
The CDT is an offical Eclipse Foundation project.
